OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers will
OL,6,Fgradually fade to leave clear spells,
OL,7,Falthough the odd shower is still
OL,8,Fpossible at times. Cloud thickens in
OL,9,Fthe early hours with rain arriving in
OL,10,Fthe west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA spell of persistent rain
OL,13,Fspreads across the region during the
OL,14,Fmorning, followed by sunny spells and
OL,15,Fscattered showers in the afternoon.
OL,16,FTurning increasingly windy through the
OL,17,Fday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
